{"tid":1960333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【胸圍抗疫】內衣廠出bra款口罩 《雙層公寓》女星搶先試戴","createTime":"2020-04-06T05:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T16:29:10.000Z","uid":333488,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"12fbaf243c0337375bb5a4b8478332bac61b0e77","tid":1960333,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐日本，當地口罩也供不應求，有內衣公司最近全面轉投生產口罩，位於當地富山縣的Atsumi Fashion，近月來在網上均有公開製作動向，更設計出胸圍款口罩引起網上熱<br />\n該廠牌近日推出胸圍款式的女性口罩，有粉紅、粉藍、淺黃、黑、白色喱士設計，曾演出人氣節目《雙層公寓》的女星近藤綾，隨即在自己的YouTube頻道作介紹，並到工場直擊及搶先試戴。日本網民對這胸圍款式口罩反應兩極，有人建議在風俗場所打工的小姐或骨妹等，可考慮在這非常時期戴上此款口罩開工，客人們應該很受落。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1k7qys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1k7qys.jpg&h=f7d2c119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOFCNMO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOFCNMO.jpg&h=daeda565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SkBFLyu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkBFLyu.jpg&h=397dc8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xjsqyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xjsqyv.jpg&h=89a65894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMq3Jkb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMq3Jkb.jpg&h=235e50f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c2ca0fc978a07ac9d41c73f4e0501c3fc76599","tid":1960333,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"話時話雙層公寓依家係咪仲拍緊定停咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無睇最新嗰季"},{"pid":"26184223e87c70e4ee2b421eb01e98d03f478ccf","tid":1960333,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,